display.title: HSS-E
description: Technically, real-life HSS-E doesn't contain Manganese, but some other HSS alloys do have Manganese, so... close enough?
&&aHSS-E&&r has some niche uses in progression.

This alloy has great durability and damage property for tools. It has the best Power multiplier (until Neutronium!) as a &&dRotor&&r for &&3Large Turbines&&r, though it's slightly less efficient than &&aHSS-S&&r.
